high_descs: Turn left, head around the counter to the right, head to the sink, turn left to face the bottle on the counter.
Pick up the plate on the counter.
Bring the plate to the microwave on the left, above the stove.
Heat the plate in the microwave.
Bring the heated plate around the kitchen to the right, past the sink, to the fridge on the left.
Put the plate in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated plate in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward to the brown shelves, turn right, go forward to the sink, turn left, go forward to the counter.
Take the white plate from the counter.
Go to the left and face the oven.
Heat the plate in the microwave above the oven.
Turn right, go forward to the counter, turn right, go forward, turn left to the fridge.
Put the plate on the top rack of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm plate in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right to go toward the sink, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the plate on the counter, to the left of the wine bottle.
Turn left, go forward, then turn right at the stove.
Heat the plate in the microwave, above the stove.
Turn right, move forward, turn right, go forward, then turn left to face the fridge.
Put the plate on the top shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm plate in the fridge.
